wikipedia_page.main: Leslie James Robert Cocker (18 September 1939 – February 2017) was an English professional footballer who played as a wing half. He played one game in the Football League for Wolverhampton Wanderers.

response: Les Cocker is the name of:
*Les Cocker (footballer, born 1924) (1924–1979), English footballer for Stockport County and Accrington Stanley
*Les Cocker (footballer, born 1939) (1939–2017), English footballer for Wolverhampton Wanderers
*Les Cocker, 77, English footballer (Wolverhampton).Death Of Youth Cup Finalist
